    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="一、准备github账号"><a href="#一、准备github账号" class="headerlink" title="一、准备github账号"></a>一、准备github账号</h1><p> 账号略</p><p>注意：如果在访问github或者通过homebrew安装软件是经常卡住，那还需要做两件事</p><p>1）homebrew切换源镜像仓库地址，一般为中科大或者清华的源</p><p>2）修改本机host文件，参考<a href="https://www.cnblogs.com/lenmom/p/9400680.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.cnblogs.com/lenmom/p/9400680.html</a></p><h1 id="二、安装nvm，npm-node-js"><a href="#二、安装nvm，npm-node-js" class="headerlink" title="二、安装nvm，npm,node js"></a>二、安装nvm，npm,node js</h1><h2 id="1-nvm安装"><a href="#1-nvm安装" class="headerlink" title="1.nvm安装"></a>1.nvm安装</h2> <figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.34.0/install.sh | bash</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>安装完成新开一个终端后输入 nvm —version检测是否安装成功</p><p>##2.安装nodejs (npm会跟着一起安装)<br>这里安装v8的最新LTS版本<br>nvm install v8.16.1<br>安装完成后输入 node -v  查看node是否安装成功；输入npm -v 查看是否安装成功</p><p>#三、安装hexo</p><p>##1.hexo以及主题安装</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#新建blog文件夹</span><br><span class="line">mkdir blog</span><br><span class="line">#安装hexo</span><br><span class="line">npm install -g hexo-cli</span><br><span class="line">#初始化博客文件夹</span><br><span class="line">hexo init</span><br><span class="line">#新建一篇博客测试下</span><br><span class="line">hexo new test</span><br><span class="line">#本地生成静态文件</span><br><span class="line">hexo g</span><br><span class="line">#选一个牛逼的主题</span><br><span class="line">git clone https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-theme-next themes/next</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>##2.配置<br>这部分内容可以参考: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/deployment.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://hexo.io/docs/deployment.html</a><br>修改_config.yml 配置文件，将hexo与个人的github关联起来，同时需要安装hexo-deployer-git插件：<br><code>npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</code></p><p>#四、绑定自己的域名<br>1.在source文件夹下建立一个CNAME文件，里面写入你的域名，例如<a href="http://www.dazhen.top" target="_blank" rel="noopener">www.dazhen.top</a></p><p>2.在github的github page设置中，填入自己的域名</p><p>#参考：</p><ul><li><a href="https://hexo.io/docs/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://hexo.io/docs/</a></li><li><a href="https://theme-next.org/docs/getting-started/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://theme-next.org/docs/getting-started/</a></li></ul>]]></content>
    
